	html {

    }
</style>

<!-- This script is to avoid links from the decorator opening in a new tab. Bug discovered on 07.10.2025. -->
<script>
(function () {
  function normalize(root) {
    if (!root) return;
    root.querySelectorAll('a[target]').forEach(a => a.removeAttribute('target'));
  }
  function init() {
    normalize(document.querySelector('#header-injection'));
    normalize(document.querySelector('#footer-injection'));

    document.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
      const a = e.target.closest('a[href]');
      if (!a) return;
      const inDecorator = e.target.closest('#header-injection, #footer-injection');
      if (!inDecorator) return;

      const href = a.getAttribute('href') || '';
      if (!href || href.startsWith('#') || href.startsWith('javascript:')) return;

      e.preventDefault();
      window.location.assign(a.href);
    }, { capture: true });
  }
  // Run after the page loads (and again if the dekorat√∏r re-renders)
  if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', init);
  } else {
    init();
  }
})();
</script>
